          <title>
            <string language="sl">Piščančki</string>
            <string language="en">Chicks</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Küken</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Poussins</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Pintainhos</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Pulcini</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Νεοσσοί</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Polluelos</string>
          </title>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <description>
            <string language="sl">Opazovanje prvih trenutkov piščančkov. Uspel sem posneti le eno fotko, ker se bojijo fleša in so zbežali stran.</string>
            <string language="en">The moment of hatching the chicks is a fantastic feeling. I could take the picture only once because the chickens were afraid of the flash and ran away.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">piščanec</string>
            <string language="en">chicken</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">jajce</string>
            <string language="en">egg</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">izvalitev</string>
            <string language="en">hatching</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Der Moment des Ausbrütens der Küken ist ein 
fantastisches Gefühl. Ich könnte das Photo nur einmal machen, 
weil die Hühner vor dem Blitz Angst hatten und weg liefen.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le moment de hacher les poussins est un sentiment
fantastique. Je pourrais prendre la photo seulement une fois 
parce que les poulets avaient peur du flash et ont fonctionné loin.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O momento de chocar os pintainhos é um 
sentimento fantástico. Eu poderia fazer exame do retrato 
somente uma vez porque as galinhas estavam receosas do flash e 
funcionavam afastado.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Il momento di covata dei pulcini è una 
sensibilità fantastica. Potrei prendere soltanto una volta 
l'immagine perché i polli erano impauriti del flash ed hanno 
funzionato via.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Η στιγμή της εκκόλαψης των νεοσσών είναι ένα 
φανταστικό συναίσθημα. Θα μπορούσα να πάρω την εικόνα μόνο
μιά φορά επειδή τα κοτόπουλα φοβήθηκαν τη λάμψη και έτρεξαν 
μακριά.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El momento de tramar los polluelos es una 
sensación fantástica. Podría tomar el cuadro solamente una 
vez porque los pollos estaban asustados del flash y se ejecutaron 
lejos.</string>
          </description>
